  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK182">
<l>aṟaṉaḻīi yallavai ceytaliṟ ṟītē</l>
<l>puṟaṉaḻīip poyttu nakai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>To smile deceitfully (in another's presence) after having reviled him to his destruction (behind his back) is a greater evil than the commission of (every other) sin and the destruction of (every) virtue.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
